WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
The ring. Hand it over.

2
00:00:03.100 --> 00:00:04.099
What?

3
00:00:04.099 --> 00:00:09.099
The wedding ring. Give it back. That emerald ring belonged to my mother.

4
00:00:09.099 --> 00:00:11.099
My wedding ring?

5
00:00:11.099 --> 00:00:13.099
Are you deaf?

6
00:00:13.099 --> 00:00:15.099
Newsflash, you've been dumped.

7
00:00:15.099 --> 00:00:16.100
Give it to me.

8
00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:19.829
No! Get off me!

9
00:00:19.829 --> 00:00:22.660
How dare you?

10
00:00:22.660 --> 00:00:24.660
Are you crazy?

11
00:00:24.660 --> 00:00:30.280
You crazy bitch.

12
00:00:30.280 --> 00:00:34.649
Get the fuck out of here.

13
00:00:34.649 --> 00:00:37.350
Now.

14
00:00:37.350 --> 00:00:38.509
Fine.

15
00:00:38.509 --> 00:00:40.700
I'll leave.

16
00:00:40.700 --> 00:00:42.799
Just so you wait.

17
00:00:42.799 --> 00:00:46.799
I'm going to get back at you. I'm going to make you pay for what you've done.

18
00:00:46.799 --> 00:00:49.340
All of you.

19
00:00:49.340 --> 00:00:51.340
Just give me the ring now.

20
00:00:52.659 --> 00:00:57.619
Here, Lydia. This belongs to you.

